+//! Comprehensive tests for the MCP server using Lab runtime patterns.
+//!
+//! These tests verify:
+//! - Request/response cycle
+//! - Tool invocation with cancellation
+//! - Resource reading with budget exhaustion
+//! - Multi-handler registration
+//! - Error handling
+
